## API Endpoints

### Authentication
- `POST /api/v1/auth/send-code` - Send sms code
- `POST /api/v1/auth/verify-code` - confirm sms code and get token
- `POST /api/v1/auth/refresh-token` - get access token
- `PATCH /api/v1/profile` - update current user's profile
- `DELETE /api/v1/delete-account` - delete current user

### Chat Rooms
- `GET /api/v1/chats` - user's all chats
- `POST /api/v1/chats` - Create chat room (private, group)
- `GET /api/v1/chats/{id}/messages` - Get messages (paginated)
- `GET /api/users/` - List users






---------------------------------------------------------------------------

- `POST /api/chat-rooms/{id}/add_members/` - Add members
- `POST /api/chat-rooms/{id}/leave/` - Leave room

### Messages
- `GET /api/messages/` - List messages
- `POST /api/messages/` - Create message
- `POST /api/messages/{id}/mark_read/` - Mark as read
- `POST /api/messages/mark_all_read/` - Mark all as read

### Users
- `GET /api/users/` - List users
- `GET /api/users/{id}/` - Get user detail


